OL,3,CTaxi driver loses licence after being
OL,4,Ccaught using mobile phone while driving
OL,6,FA taxi driver from Buckinghamshire
OL,7,Fhas lost his appeal against a decision
OL,8,Fto revoke his license after he was
OL,9,Fcaught using a mobile phone whilst
OL,10,Fdriving.
OL,12,FMr Azhar Iqbal of Littleworth Road,
OL,13,FHigh Wycombe, was stopped on the A355
OL,14,Fby police, after he was seen handling
OL,15,Fand speaking into a mobile phone
OL,16,Fwhilst driving in August 2022.
OL,18,FMr Iqbal failed to notify
OL,19,FBuckinghamshire Council at the time of
OL,20,Fthe offence, contrary to the
OL,21,Fconditions of his private hire licence.
