OL,6,FHe eventually notified the council's
OL,7,FLicensing Team in April 2023, and
OL,8,Fsubsequently Mr Iqbal's private hire
OL,9,Flicence was revoked by Buckinghamshire
OL,10,FCouncil on 12 October 2023.
