OL,6,FMr Iqbal unsuccessfully attempted to
OL,7,Fhave his original conviction
OL,8,Foverturned. On 19 December 2023, after
OL,9,Fhearing evidence from the attending
OL,10,Fpolice officers and watching
OL,11,Frecordings from officers' body worn
OL,12,Fcameras, magistrates said they were
OL,13,Fsatisfied that he was guilty of the
OL,14,Foffence.
OL,16,FHe was issued with 6 DVLA points and
OL,17,Fordered to pay a fine and court costs
OL,18,Ftotalling #774.
