OL,4,Ccaught using mobile phone while driving
OL,6,FFurther to Mr Iqbal's revocation,
OL,7,FBuckinghamshire Council received an
OL,8,Fappeal against the decision to revoke
OL,9,Fhis licence which was heard at Wycombe
OL,10,FMagistrates on Friday 26 April 2024.
OL,12,FThe District Judge found the
OL,13,Fconviction for using a mobile phone
OL,14,Fwas sufficient to justify revoking Mr
OL,15,FIqbal's licence in accordance with the
OL,16,Fcouncil's policy and that there were
OL,17,Fno exceptional circumstances to
OL,18,Fjustify an alternative decision.
