OL,6,F"It is a significant distraction and
OL,7,Fsubstantially increases the risk of
OL,8,Fthe driver crashing ` putting
OL,9,Fpassengers, pedestrians, and other
OL,10,Froad users at risk of serious harm.
OL,11,FImportantly, the handling of mobile
OL,12,Fphones while driving is completely
OL,13,Favoidable and there are many hands-
OL,14,Ffree solutions available.
