OL,6,F"The council expects its licensed
OL,7,Fdrivers to maintain professional
OL,8,Fstandards, comply with the law and
OL,9,Fprotect public safety. Licensed
OL,10,Fdrivers who are found driving while
OL,11,Fusing a phone by hand can expect to
OL,12,Fhave their licence revoked in line
OL,13,Fwith our policy."
